{"item_id":"21a8ca8aca:0","text":"每个人都知道 Black 和 White colors 在 rendering 中意味着什么，对吧？"}
{"item_id":"21a8ca8aca:1","text":"当然！"}
{"item_id":"21a8ca8aca:2","text":"嗯……以防万一，这里有一份快速指南，说明 RenderMan 在 Roughness、Metallic 和 Bump 中如何处理 Black 与 White values。"}
{"item_id":"21a8ca8aca:3","text":"材质粗糙度（Material Roughness）"}
{"item_id":"21a8ca8aca:4","text":"黑色（Black）= 光亮表面（Shiny）"}
{"item_id":"21a8ca8aca:5","text":"Roughness Value（粗糙度值）：1"}
{"item_id":"21a8ca8aca:6","text":"白色（White）= 粗糙表面（Rough）"}
{"item_id":"21a8ca8aca:7","text":"Roughness Value（粗糙度值）：0"}
{"item_id":"21a8ca8aca:8","text":"材质 Metallic 工作流（Material Metallic Workflow）"}
{"item_id":"21a8ca8aca:9","text":"黑色（Black）= 非金属（Non-Metal）"}
{"item_id":"21a8ca8aca:10","text":"Roughness Value（粗糙度值）：1"}
{"item_id":"21a8ca8aca:11","text":"白色（White）= 金属（Metal）"}
{"item_id":"21a8ca8aca:12","text":"Roughness Value（粗糙度值）：0"}
{"item_id":"21a8ca8aca:13","text":"Bump Maps（凹凸贴图）"}
{"item_id":"21a8ca8aca:14","text":"黑色（Black）= 向内凹凸（Bump In）"}
{"item_id":"21a8ca8aca:15","text":"白色（White）= 向外凹凸（Bump Out）"}
{"item_id":"21a8ca8aca:16","text":"Displacement Maps（置换贴图）"}
{"item_id":"21a8ca8aca:17","text":"黑色（Black）= 向内置换（Displace Inwards）"}
{"item_id":"21a8ca8aca:18","text":"白色（White）= 向外置换（Displace Outwards）"}
{"item_id":"21a8ca8aca:19","text":"Presence（Opacity，不透明度）"}
{"item_id":"21a8ca8aca:20","text":"黑色（Black）= OFF（关闭）"}
{"item_id":"21a8ca8aca:21","text":"白色（White）= ON（开启）"}
